Euro Weakens on Speculation Greece’s Sovereign Debt Crisis Set to Worsen

-- B y   N i c h o l a s   R e y n o l d s
-- 
2011-06-14T00:34:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/euro-falls-versus-yen-dollar-on-concern-greece-s-debt-crisis-will-worsen.html
The euro fell against the yen and
the dollar on concern European Union finance ministers meeting
today will struggle to resolve  Greece ’s debt crisis.  The single currency weakened to 115.35 yen as of 9:32 a.m.
in  Tokyo  from 115.65 yen yesterday in  New York . The currency
declined to $1.4392 from $1.4413.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nicholas Reynolds at 
 nreynolds2@bloomberg.net  